Package: pagoda3
Title: An Agent-Driven Browser Viewer for Single-Cell Data (via L*/lstar)
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Peter", "Kharchenko", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "peter.kharchenko@gmail.com")
Description: Launcher and browsable-store preparation for the pagoda3 single-cell viewer.
    The viewer is a browser app; this package turns a single-cell object (or an L* store) into
    something it opens fast and launches it locally. lstar is the substrate (format conversion and
    compute kernels); pagoda3 owns the viewer policy (which navigators to precompute).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: lstar (>= 0.2.0), Matrix, methods, stats, utils
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
